{"tid":1037983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教科書刪陳勝吳廣範文 疑滅絕起義意識","createTime":"2019-02-26T10:31:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T05:43:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"084e3a5cafa0cbfde3625cb2cee52de158d7c884","tid":1037983,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T10:31:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190226/20620706\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190226%2F20620706&d=%2BPHBpHGgTFxyg2LnQdSnfWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=01300e55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190226%2F20620706&h=d6463ea8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190226/20620706</a><br />\n<br />\n教科書刪陳勝吳廣範文 疑滅絕起義意識<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190226/large/a1303a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190226%2Flarge%2Fa1303a.gif&h=b2af9c1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「陳勝吳廣起義」插畫。<br />\n<br />\n「苟富貴，勿相忘」等耳熟能詳名句出自《史記》名篇《陳涉世家》，相關章節多年來一直是內地語文教科書的課文。不過最新版初中語文教科書已刪除《陳涉世家》。課文題材講述底層民眾陳勝、吳廣起義，惹人聯想。<br />\n<br />\n中國教育部自2017年起統一編寫語文、歷史等教材，供所有小學與初中今年起使用。近日騰訊歷史主編撰文指，翻查最新版中一至中三的初中語文教材，確實找不到《陳涉世家》。課文記述陳勝、吳廣等底層民眾起義反抗秦朝暴政的歷史，被視為官逼民反典型歷史。未刪前被收錄在中三語文教材，部份段落要求學生背誦， 「今亡亦死，舉大計亦死，等死，死國可乎？」等名句為人所熟悉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190226/large/a1303b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190226%2Flarge%2Fa1303b.gif&h=3c209bfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n教研員：新教材培育剛直人格<br />\n<br />\n同樣出自《史記》的《周亞夫軍細柳》則被編入新教材。內容講述漢文帝劉恒慰問名將周亞夫的部隊受刁難，不像其他軍隊般逢迎討好，強調周亞夫治軍嚴明、忠於職守。重慶市教科院語文教研員陳家堯表示，《周》入選教材較《陳》好，因有利於培育學生剛直的人格。<br />\n<br />\n《陳涉世家》1960年左右被收錄入語文教科書，惟近60年來亦曾被短暫刪除。例如因六七十年代盛行「儒法鬥爭」被刪；文革時期舊教材成批判對象，各地教材大幅度壓縮文言文空間。直到1978年文革結束、中學教育恢復正軌，《陳》再次入選教材。<br />\n<br />\n事件引起網民熱議，有人聯想當局要滅絕任何「起義」的意識，有人慨嘆今後學生「還知道『王侯將相寧有種乎』嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n新浪網/中央社  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n儲量全球第一 勘探開發難"},{"pid":"01881e84ad7e4790f2bcbaf45ede2b4732fd2883","tid":1037983,"uid":47259,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:45:03.000Z","msg":"四大名著要bam曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9427e37bd1111d3db5af8102e6148d548fa62a1","tid":1037983,"uid":51920,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:52:59.000Z","msg":"內容講述漢文帝劉恒慰問名將周亞夫的部隊受刁難，不像其他軍隊般逢迎討好<br />\n<br />\n唔知年羹堯點死?"},{"pid":"6422ae8730d7029d97ec4565ab8ec9e8d248cf1d","tid":1037983,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:58:06.000Z","msg":"支那狗係唔應該識歷史架<br />\n支那做番狗得架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0c909575980010d2abdbb94aaf9d135e8184a3","tid":1037983,"uid":61280,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T15:04:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">索性Cut晒佢，秦始蝗傳位毛神，並指定四傳至永帝算9數把啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到時一版紙讀完支那屎，個個100分Happy Together！！！</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6728ed0d8040d36c583c68c5e3c1c7f319705530","tid":1037983,"uid":7436,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T15:13:54.000Z","msg":"newspeak<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33313575c99cf2c2587bb1b53cbf5377584fd161","tid":1037983,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci